description: Webportal to Angkor Wat and Siem Reap
overview:
This webportal is the perfect guide to prepare your trip to Cambodia and especially to the city of Siem Reap, gateway to the magnificent Angkor Wat.

It will offer you all the information you are looking for about the temples and the historical sites, the several others sightseeing you cannot miss, the travel tips and requirements like visa, vaccinations, climate, airport and way to move around, as well as the emergency contacts that you will need in case of trouble.

Find also the best hotels deals if you are an independent traveler, some of the best travel agents in town, the finest restaurants to discover the Khmer cuisine and plats from all over the world, the lively nightlife with those bars and clubs, the best shopping addresses for souvenir and fashion, the smoothest massage salons and Spa to get pampered, the different sports you can practice and activities for your recreation, and an helpful forum for your eventual questions and to check amazing pictures of Cambodia.
